20:43.065 --> 20:44.283
Aah!

20:44.525 --> 20:46.158
Aaah!

20:46.193 --> 20:47.793
T-Thank you.

20:47.828 --> 20:49.128
You're killing me!

20:49.163 --> 20:51.029
Thank you!

20:51.065 --> 20:53.265
- "Ooshi," no!
- We should... We should... Let's...

20:53.300 --> 20:56.335
Let's... Yeah. Let's get
