20:56.370 --> 21:00.072
You know, this whole thing
has showed me that you and I,

21:00.107 --> 21:02.107
w-we're kind of a team, too.

21:02.143 --> 21:03.675
We're kind of like...

21:03.711 --> 21:06.779
We're kind of like
boyfriend and girlfriend.

21:06.814 --> 21:08.647
Yeah, I know, Jim.

21:08.682 --> 21:10.849
- You do?
- Mm-hmm.

21:10.885 --> 21:12.518
How long have you known that?

21:12.553 --> 21:14.453
Mm...

21:14.488 --> 21:16.155
when I stopped paying
for your hotel room

21:16.190 --> 21:18.991
'cause you were sleeping
at my apartment every night.

21:19.026 --> 21:21.627
So, wait. A-Are we living together?

21:22.696 --> 21:25.097
If it offends your
delicate sensibilities,

21:25.132 --> 21:27.599
